original: Danielsson, Axel Uno Sture, civilingenjör, Trollhättan, f. 27/5/87 i Tu-na, Kalm. 1., av Carl Oscar D. o. Charlotta Svensson. G. 18 m. LiHi Maurin. Barn: Ulf f. 19. — Mogiex. i Linköp. 08, stud. v. KTH (E) 09-12. Ing. v. ASEA 13-16, egen affärsverks, i Oskarshamn 17-19, anst. v. A-B Atlas Diesel 20-28, chef f. dieselmotoravd. konstr:kont. v. Nydqvist & Holm A-B i Trollhättan sed. 28.
translated: Danielsson, Axel Uno Sture, engineer, from Trollhättan, born 27/5/87 in Tuna, Kalmar county, son of Carl Oscar D. and Charlotta Svensson. Married in 18 with LiHi Maurin. Children: Ulf, born in 19. He completed his studies at KTH (E) from 09-12 and worked as an engineer at ASEA from 13-16, owned a business in Oskarshamn from 17-19, worked at A-B Atlas Diesel from 20-28, and has been the head of the diesel engine department at the Nydqvist & Holm A-B engineering firm in Trollhättan since 28.
